messages.content:
你是 marketting-planning 项目的 attribute agent。
只围绕当前多轮营销规划链路归因：request_normalization、intent_recognition、field_clarification、session_merge、path_dispatch、planning_function、result_assembly、sse_generation、adapter_extraction。
优先定位最早造成 planning 输出不满足 reference contract 的阶段；如果 target_value_unit_probe、execution_stage_probe 或 planning_output_probe 已复现错误，必须以这些探针证据作为高优先级根因依据。
只能输出 AttributeResult JSON 所需字段；证据不足时用 evidence_strength=none/weak 和 root_cause_hypothesis 表达缺口。
最终只输出 AttributeResult JSON 所需字段：expectation_attributions、suspected_locations、root_cause_hypothesis、evidence、evidence_strength。

## 输出约束：attribute 归因分析输出
你的输出必须是合法 JSON，且严格符合以下 JSON Schema：
```json
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "expectation_attributions": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {
        "$ref": "#/$defs/ExpectationAttribution"
      },
      "minItems": 1
    },
    "suspected_locations": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {}
    },
    "root_cause_hypothesis": {
      "type": "string",
      "minLength": 1
    },
    "evidence": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {}
    },
    "evidence_strength": {
      "type": "string",
      "minLength": 1
    }
  },
  "additionalProperties": false,
  "$defs": {
    "ExpectationAttribution": {
      "type": "object",
      "properties": {
        "expectation_id": {
          "type": "string",
          "minLength": 1
        },
        "fulfillment_status": {
          "type": "string",
          "minLength": 1
        },
        "suspected_locations": {
          "type": "array",
          "items": {}
        },
        "root_cause_hypothesis": {
          "type": "string",
          "minLength": 1
        },
        "evidence": {
          "type": "array",
          "items": {}
        }
      },
      "additionalProperties": false,
      "required": [
        "expectation_id",
        "fulfillment_status"
      ]
    }
  },
  "required": [
    "expectation_attributions",
    "root_cause_hypothesis"
  ]
}
```

### 强约束
- 最终回答必须只包含一个 JSON object；不要输出 Markdown，不要使用 ```json 代码块，不要在 JSON 外输出解释、前缀或后缀。
- 最终回答首字符必须是 `{`，末字符必须是 `}`。
- JSON 字符串内部如需引用用户原词，禁止直接写未转义英文双引号；请使用中文引号“”或转义为 `\"`。
- 必须包含 `required` 列表中的所有字段。
- 每个字段值必须匹配 schema 中的类型。
- 以下字段必须非空（空字符串/空数组/空对象/None 均视为不合规，会被阻断）：['expectation_attributions', 'root_cause_hypothesis']
- `additionalProperties: false`：禁止输出 schema 未定义的字段。
- 禁止把 schema 里的类型描述符（如 "string"）原样当作内容填进去——每个字段必须填入真实内容。

{
  "expectation_attributions": [
    {
      "expectation_id": "意图识别准确性",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": [
        "intent_recognition stage",
        "intent classification model/prompt"
      ],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "意图分类模型/提示词未能将用户关于“NBEV目标、增加理财师、优化产品方案”的查询识别为营销规划相关意图，错误分类为“其他意图”(4001)，导致无法满足预期。",
      "evidence": [
        "raw_response 中 intent_name 为“其他意图”，intent 为“4001”",
        "execution_stage_probe 在 intent_recognition 阶段 evidence 显示 actual_stage=non_agent 与 expected_stage=intent 不符"
      ]
    },
    {
      "expectation_id": "阶段路由正确性",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": [
        "intent_recognition stage",
        "routing logic based on intent output"
      ],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "由于意图分类错误，intent_recognition 阶段生成了 stage=non_agent，导致请求被错误路由到 non_agent 分支，无法进入正常的 intent/planning 阶段。",
      "evidence": [
        "output_summary 中 stage 为 non_agent",
        "execution_trace 中 intent_recognition 证据证实 actual_stage=non_agent"
      ]
    },
    {
      "expectation_id": "mp_contract:expected_stage",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": [
        "intent_recognition stage"
      ],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "与阶段路由正确性相同，intent_recognition 阶段未能产出 expected_stage=intent，导致整体 reference_contract 不满足。",
      "evidence": [
        "execution_stage_probe 中 expected_stage=intent，但 actual_stage=non_agent",
        "planning_output_probe 显示 stage_match=false，actual_stage 缺失"
      ]
    }
  ],
  "suspected_locations": [
    {
      "stage": "intent_recognition",
      "discrepancy": "actual_stage=non_agent, expected_stage=intent",
      "probe": "execution_stage_probe"
    },
    {
      "file": "app/workflow/steps/intent_recognition.py",
      "reason": "intent classification logic"
    },
    {
      "file": "app/workflow/prompts/intent_prompt.py",
      "reason": "prompt that fails to recognize NBEV/planning intent"
    }
  ],
  "root_cause_hypothesis": "在 intent_recognition 阶段，意图分类模型/提示词未能正确理解用户关于补足 NBEV 目标的营销规划意图，错误地将 query 分类为“其他意图”(4001)，导致 stage 输出为 non_agent，进而使整个请求偏离预期的 intent/planning 链路，造成核心期望未满足。",
  "evidence": [
    {
      "source": "raw_response",
      "content": "intent: '4001', intent_name: '其他意图'"
    },
    {
      "source": "execution_stage_probe",
      "stage": "intent_recognition",
      "actual_stage": "non_agent",
      "expected_stage": "intent"
    },
    {
      "source": "planning_output_probe",
      "stage_match": false,
      "actual_stage": null
    },
    {
      "source": "output_summary",
      "stage": "non_agent"
    }
  ],
  "evidence_strength": "strong"
}

